<emphasis id="C4C82D5DFFC45078FF19820EFE9CF935" bold="true" box="[151,275,1643,1667]" pageId="1" pageNumber="585">FIGURE 1.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="31BC8ACCFFC45078FE97820EFD73F935" authority="van der Weele, 1909" authorityName="van der Weele" authorityYear="1909" box="[281,764,1643,1667]" class="Insecta" family="Corydalidae" genus="Neochauliodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Megaloptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="borneensis">
<emphasis id="C4C82D5DFFC45078FE97820EFDABF935" box="[281,548,1643,1667]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="585">Neochauliodes borneensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="922D8CBEFFC45078FDA48209FD73F935" author="van der Weele, H. W." box="[554,764,1643,1667]" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" pagination="249 - 264" refId="ref3530" refString="van der Weele, H. W. (1909) New genera and species of Megaloptera Latr. Notes from the Leyden Museum, 30, 249 - 264." type="journal article" year="1909">van der Weele, 1909</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, female from Palawan, the Philippines. Scale bar: 5.0 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<subSubSection id="BEA6A2C4FFC45078FF4982D6FBAEF871" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" type="description">
<paragraph id="F603F14FFFC45078FF4982D6FBECF881" blockId="1.[151,1437,1715,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="585">
<emphasis id="C4C82D5DFFC45078FF4982D6FD8AF97D" bold="true" box="[199,517,1715,1739]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" reason="1">Supplementary description.</emphasis>
Specimen from 
<collectingRegion id="34783FADFFC45078FD3582D6FC96F97D" box="[699,793,1715,1739]" country="Philippines" name="Palawan" pageId="1" pageNumber="585">Palawan</collectingRegion>
. Female. Body length 
<quantity id="31445CAAFFC45078FB9E82D6FBFBF97D" box="[1040,1140,1715,1739]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.63" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" unit="mm" value="16.3">16.3 mm</quantity>
; forewing length 
<quantity id="31445CAAFFC45078FABB82D6FA17F97D" box="[1333,1432,1715,1739]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.42" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" unit="mm" value="24.2">24.2 mm</quantity>
, hindwing length 
<quantity id="31445CAAFFC45078FEC782B2FE25F959" box="[329,426,1751,1775]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.21" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" unit="mm" value="22.1">22.1 mm</quantity>
. Head with a pair of blackish markings posterolaterally, and with a blackish stripe medially. Left forewing with distal half damaged. Forewing markings mostly distinct and isolated from each other. Stem and proximal half of two main branches of forewing MP brown. Four forewing radial crossveins present.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F603F14FFFC45078FF5E8326FBAEF871" blockId="1.[151,1437,1715,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="585">Specimen from Mindanao. Female. Body length 17.0 mm; forewing length 31.0 mm, hindwing length 27.0 mm. Head with a pair of blackish markings posterolaterally, and with a blackish stripe medially. Wings partly damaged. Forewing markings much fewer, but mostly distinct and isolated from each other. Stem and proximal half of two main branches of forewing MP pale yellow. Five or six forewing radial crossveins present.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
